# Format Time

- Initiated by Phrase: "Format Time", "Formatted Time" or alias "FT"
- Use mcp-datetime to retrieve `get_datetime`
- `TimeZone` is Always `PDT`
- Return only the formatted time string
- Convert `get_datetime` to format: "MM.DD.YY | HH:MM AM/PM `TimeZone`"
